OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSix Nations: Wales-Ireland 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fkit clash frustrates       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fcolour-blind fans          
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, "They should be doing it for the fans. 
OL,6, I don't see why it would make a        
OL,7, difference what colour they wear."     
OL,9,FJimmy Griffin, 23, who is colour blind,
OL,10,Fis frustrated by Wales and Ireland's   
OL,11,Fdecision to play in their traditional  
OL,12,Fjerseys in Saturday's Six Nations game,
OL,13,Fdespite guidance aimed at avoiding kit 
OL,14,Fclashes.                               
OL,16,FHe said a kit change would make a big  
OL,17,Fdifference to colour-blind people.     
OL,19,FThe Welsh and Irish rugby unions said  
OL,20,Fthey were committed to being inclusive.
